recitals:
,
Having regard to Article 18 of the Treaty establishing the European Coal and Steel Community,
Whereas the Consultative Committee of the European Coal and Steel Community, whose term of office expired on 3 March 1998, should be renewed;
Whereas in the first place the representative organisations of producers and workers, which are required to draw up lists of twice as many candidates as there are seats allotted to them, should be designated;
Whereas notifications have been sent by the Governments of the Member States;
